Great! That was attacked little lesson
wasn't it? We've practiced different ways

00:11:01.330 --> 00:11:03.300
to greet new people,

00:11:03.300 --> 00:11:09.460
introduce yourself and respond to
introductions. We've also practiced

00:11:09.460 --> 00:11:16.580
